data.title: Apartment 24
data.text:
Rent an apartment in Kollbrunn

The small picturesque village of Kollbrunn with its approx. 2500 inhabitants is part of the municipality of Zell in the Winterthur district of the Canton of Zurich. Kollbrun borders on the municipalities of Schlatt, Kyburg and Weisslingen and thus offers good access to these municipalities.

Rent an apartment in Stadt Zürich

Rent an apartment in Glattbrugg

Glattbrugg is located in the Glattal, between Zurich and the airport Kloten. Glattal is one of the most dynamic regions in Switzerland. The wide range of leisure, educational and transport facilities in the region and in the neighbouring city of Zurich make Glattbrugg very attractive. It is one of the strongest economic regions in Switzerland.

Rent an apartment in Winterthur

Winterthur is already a larger city. With around 112,000 inhabitants, Winterthur is the sixth largest city in Switzerland and the second largest in the Canton of Zurich. Winterthur used to be an important industrial city. Today it is a city with cultural diversity and affordable living space. Zurich Airport is 15 kilometres away from Winterthur railway station.

Rent an apartment in Schlieren

Schlieren has developed very rapidly in recent years. Schlieren is a place with an old city centre, the city park and the new quarters. The city has an excellent location, directly bordering Zurich. The Zurich main railway station is only 12 minutes away by S-Bahn.

Rent an apartment in Utzenstorf

Rent an apartment in Baar

Baar is the second largest municipality in Canton Zug. Our furnished, bright rooms are located in a favorable tax area near Zug and Zurich. The express trains stop in Baar. With the city railway you reach Zug city every 15 minutes with connection to the national and international rail network.
